{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-practice-numbers-11-to-19/task-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-practice-numbers-11-to-19","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Pitanje traži brojeve u rastućoj sekvenci, što znači od najmanjeg do najvećeg. Ispravna sekvenca je <ruby>十六<rp>(</rp><rt>shí liù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十七<rp>(</rp><rt>shí qī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十八<rp>(</rp><rt>shí bā</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>, koja odgovara 16, 17 i 18.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ovo vežbanje nema audio. Molimo vas da pročitate pitanje ispod i odaberete tačan odgovor.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-practice-numbers-11-to-19/task-4"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koji izbor ima broj u seriji <strong>rastanja</strong>?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><ruby>十一<rp>(</rp><rt>shí yī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十<rp>(</rp><rt>shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十五<rp>(</rp><rt>shí wǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovi brojevi su 11, 10 i 15. Oni nisu u rastućoj sekvenci jer je 10 manje od 11.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><ruby>十六<rp>(</rp><rt>shí liù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十七<rp>(</rp><rt>shí qī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十八<rp>(</rp><rt>shí bā</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><ruby>十四<rp>(</rp><rt>shí sì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十三<rp>(</rp><rt>shí sān</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十二<rp>(</rp><rt>shí èr</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></p>","feedback":"<p>Ovi brojevi su 14, 13 i 12. Nalaze se u opadajućoj sekvenci, a ne u rastućoj.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><ruby>十九<rp>(</rp><rt>shí jiǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十七<rp>(</rp><rt>shí qī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>十五<rp>(</rp><rt>shí wǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></r